title: Tony Travers on the Labour leadership contest
itunes:author: Professor Tony Travers, Martin Rogers
description: Contributor(s): Professor Tony Travers, Martin Rogers | With the Labour leadership contest becoming perhaps the key British political story of the summer, we sat down with Professor Tony Travers to discuss the candidates, the contest so far and its implications for the future of the party and the UK’s overall political landscape.
